skillset required
1. problem solving skills
	- to remove bottlenecks
	- more problems to solve and different types of problems to solve
2. Technologies
	- learn wide variety of technologies e.g. caches, load balancers, proxy servers, API gateways
	- breakdown the similar tech stacks, compare them
	- aware of the latest technologies in the market
	- any complex systems faces different challenges like failures, bottlenecks, outages
	- ==the problems need to be pre-identified and solved way before the even happened==
3. Planning and pre-planning
	- prepare detailed plans and documentation by pre-empting the issues that may happen in the future
	- this will give the blueprint the team to execute the vision
4. Scalability
	- think in terms of system and scalability
	- practice
